apps.name: Youtube (Cercube+Extra)
apps.subtitle: Cercube with extra features!
apps.versionDescription:
Current YouTube IPA: `v18.20.3`
Current Cercube Version: `v5.3.11`
Current App Compatibility: `iOS/iPadOS 14.0` or later

RELEASE F1: (May 25th 2023)
• Updated YouTube from `v18.18.2` to `v18.20.3`
• Updated YTNoModernUI
   • Implemented Red Progress Bar (based off of 16.42.3)
   • Implemented Old Buffer Bar (based off of 16.42.3)
   • Implemented Older YouTube Version 16.42.3

Issues in this Release:

• Options “Enable Share Button” & “Enable ‘Save to Playlist’ Button” don’t work correctly.
• [Cercube Exclusive] • Cercube Download Tab & Cercube Menu not working with YouTube's New Dark Mode
• Live Videos/Streams Crashing / Live Chat Messages Invisible (#39)
• Hide Shorts Videos not working Correctly (#38)
• OLED/OLD Dark Theme Options Not Working (Workaround: use this version of CercubePlusExtra: v18.20.3•5.3.11)
